## 🛠 Teknoloji Stack

**Core:**
- Next.js 14+ (App Router)
- TypeScript 5.5+ (Strict Mode)
- Tailwind CSS 3.4+
- shadcn/ui + Radix UI

**Features:**
- next-intl (5 dil: EN, DE, TR, FR, PT)
- next-themes (light/dark/system)
- Web Crypto API + qrcode

---

## 📁 Klasör Yapısı

```
app/[locale]/          # Dil-bazlı routing
  ├── layout.tsx       # Ana layout
  ├── page.tsx         # Ana sayfa
  └── tools/           # Tool sayfaları (8 tool)
components/
  ├── ui/              # shadcn/ui (button, card, etc.)
  ├── layout/          # Layout (header, footer, theme)
  └── tools/           # Tool components
i18n/locales/         # 5 translation dosyası
lib/                  # Utils (crypto, color, tools-data)
hooks/                # Custom hooks
types/                # TypeScript types
```

---

## 🎨 Naming Conventions

| Tip | Convention | Örnek |
|-----|-----------|-------|
| Components | PascalCase | `ToolCard.tsx` |
| Files | kebab-case | `use-theme.ts` |
| Folders | kebab-case | `json-formatter/` |
| Variables | camelCase | `handleClick` |
| Constants | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE | `SAMPLE_JSON` |
| Types | PascalCase | `Tool`, `RGB` |

---

## 📝 TypeScript Kuralları

### Path Aliases
```typescript
@/* → ./*
@/components/* → ./components/*
@/lib/* → ./lib/*

// Kullanım
import { Button } from '@/components';
import { cn } from '@/lib/utils';
```

### Type Safety
```typescript
// ✅ DOĞRU
interface Props {
  title: string;
  onSubmit: (value: string) => void;
}

// ❌ YANLIŞ
interface Props {
  title: any;
  onSubmit: Function;
}
```

---

## 🌍 Internationalization (i18n)

### KRİTİK KURAL: NO HARD-CODED STRINGS!

```typescript
// ✅ DOĞRU
const t = useTranslations('tools.toolName');
const tc = useTranslations('common');

<h1>{t('title')}</h1>
<Button>{tc('loadSample')}</Button>

// ❌ YANLIŞ
<h1>Tool Title</h1>
<Button>Load Sample</Button>
```

### Translation Pattern
```typescript
// Tool-specific
const t = useTranslations('tools.toolName');

// Common (shared across tools)
const tc = useTranslations('common');
```

### 5 Dil Desteği
Her yeni string için:
1. `i18n/locales/en.json` (base)
2. `i18n/locales/de.json`
3. `i18n/locales/tr.json`
4. `i18n/locales/fr.json`
5. `i18n/locales/pt.json`

---

## 🚨 Common Mistakes & Fixes

### 1. useCopyToClipboard Hook
```typescript
// ❌ YANLIŞ - Returns object, not array!
const [, copy] = useCopyToClipboard();

// ✅ DOĞRU
const { copy } = useCopyToClipboard();
const { copied, copy } = useCopyToClipboard();
```

### 2. Slider onValueChange Type
```typescript
// ❌ YANLIŞ - Implicit any
onValueChange={([value]) => setValue(value)}

// ✅ DOĞRU - Explicit type
onValueChange={([value]: number[]) => setValue(value)}
```

### 3. Hard-coded Strings
```typescript
// ❌ YANLIŞ
<Button>Click Here</Button>
<h1>Tool Title</h1>

// ✅ DOĞRU
<Button>{t('clickHere')}</Button>
<h1>{t('title')}</h1>
```

### 4. Missing Radix UI Packages
```bash
# Checkbox kullanıyorsan:
npm install @radix-ui/react-checkbox

# Slider kullanıyorsan:
npm install @radix-ui/react-slider

# Label kullanıyorsan:
npm install @radix-ui/react-label
```

