## 🚀 Yeni Tool Ekleme (Quick Guide)

### 1. Klasör Oluştur
```bash
mkdir -p app/[locale]/tools/tool-name
```

### 2. Page Template
```typescript
'use client';

import * as React from 'react';
import { useTranslations } from 'next-intl';
import { Button, Card, CardHeader, CardTitle, CardContent } from '@/components';

export default function ToolNamePage() {
  const t = useTranslations('tools.toolName');
  const tc = useTranslations('common');
  
  return (
    <div className="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
      <div className="mb-8">
        <h1 className="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">{t('title')}</h1>
        <p className="text-muted-foreground">{t('description')}</p>
      </div>
      
      <Card>
        <CardHeader>
          <CardTitle>{t('input')}</CardTitle>
        </CardHeader>
        <CardContent>
          {/* Tool logic */}
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
    </div>
  );
}
```

### 3. Translation (5 dil!)
```json
// i18n/locales/en.json
{
  "tools": {
    "toolName": {
      "title": "Tool Title",
      "description": "Description",
      "input": "Input",
      "output": "Output"
    }
  }
}
```

### 4. Ana Sayfaya Ekle
```typescript
// app/[locale]/page.tsx
{
  id: 'tool-name',
  title: t('tools.toolName.title'),
  description: t('tools.toolName.description'),
  category: 'generators', // encoders, formatters, converters, text, utilities
  icon: 'IconName', // lucide-react
  href: `/${params.locale}/tools/tool-name`,
}
```

### 5. Test
```bash
npm run type-check  # 0 errors
npm run lint        # 0 warnings
# Test 5 dilde + dark mode
```

